{"tid":381034,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"到底點解瞓係床上 尿意會比較強","createTime":"2017-08-30T15:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T10:30:03.000Z","uid":109889,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21fc47b75df489f2d8461a210f6a2ad9eb36fae7","tid":381034,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"呢個問題已經糾纏咗我好幾年<br />\n上Google 啲人淨係話係尿道感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但明明成個情況完全唔似係感染或者發炎<br />\n<br />\n每次一攤落床就會好想去廁所<br />\n去完如果唔係即刻瞓 10幾分鍾之後就會想再去<br />\n不斷loop<br />\n唔瞓係床就冇事 瞓sofa瞓地下都冇野<br />\n<br />\n問好多朋友都有呢啲情況出現<br />\n但到底點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89958b11a974c6c2d99cda069c04f72ef035b019","tid":381034,"uid":33031,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"心理作用，屬強逼症一種"},{"pid":"6b6e662e8553f6e07ca97b482f0054ca38d5e73a","tid":381034,"uid":45461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"放鬆，放鬆埋個 sphincter"},{"pid":"ab3adb70293f4c0e40605365f30b72f575a9f57d","tid":381034,"uid":109889,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心理作用，屬強逼症一種</blockquote><br />\n試緊忍住死都唔會去<br />\n但一定會半夜醒之後焗住要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果死忍係咪會遲早會冇咗呢個問題"},{"pid":"0e081c129a026bdb542319a83e3deed37db7a1a4","tid":381034,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放鬆，放鬆埋個 sphincter</blockquote><br />\n隨時瀨埋屎俾你睇添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06c7d446e039baf4eae2ea83d87b8a937e45d99","tid":381034,"uid":33031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"每次去都柯好多就係唔正常<br />\n每次少少就試下忍，係你心癮姐"},{"pid":"ea2b597f17f91633c3942ee25a7dd088bf6e33dc","tid":381034,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":